home buyers guide will help you understand every step involved in the homebuying process and ensure that it goes smoothly.\r\n'),(1511,70,'_main-content','field_5afa9f11ebf40'),(1512,70,'chapters_0_image','35'),(1513,70,'_chapters_0_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1514,70,'chapters_0_title','Chapter 1'),(1515,70,'_chapters_0_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1516,70,'chapters_0_content','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(1517,70,'_chapters_0_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1518,70,'chapters_1_image','36'),(1519,70,'_chapters_1_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1520,70,'chapters_1_title','Chapter 2'),(1521,70,'_chapters_1_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1522,70,'chapters_1_content','Best Investment  Destinations to Buy a Home'),(1523,70,'_chapters_1_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1524,70,'chapters_2_image','37'),(1525,70,'_chapters_2_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1526,70,'chapters_2_title','Chapter 3'),(1527,70,'_chapters_2_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1528,70,'chapters_2_content','Types of Residential  Property'),(1529,70,'_chapters_2_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1530,70,'chapters_3_image','30'),(1531,70,'_chapters_3_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1532,70,'chapters_3_title','Chapter 4'),(1533,70,'_chapters_3_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1534,70,'chapters_3_content','Things to Check Before Booking a Home'),(1535,70,'_chapters_3_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1536,70,'chapters_4_image','31'),(1537,70,'_chapters_4_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1538,70,'chapters_4_title','Chapter 5'),(1539,70,'_chapters_4_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1540,70,'chapters_4_content','Documents Required to  Buy a House'),(1541,70,'_chapters_4_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1542,70,'chapters_5_image','32'),(1543,70,'_chapters_5_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1544,70,'chapters_5_title','Chapter 6'),(1545,70,'_chapters_5_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1546,70,'chapters_5_content','The Complete Home Loan Application Process'),(1547,70,'_chapters_5_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1548,70,'chapters_6_image','33'),(1549,70,'_chapters_6_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1550,70,'chapters_6_title','Chapter 7'),(1551,70,'_chapters_6_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1552,70,'chapters_6_content','How to Save Taxes on a  Real Estate Investment'),(1553,70,'_chapters_6_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1554,70,'chapters_7_image','34'),(1555,70,'_chapters_7_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1556,70,'chapters_7_title','Chapter 8'),(1557,70,'_chapters_7_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1558,70,'chapters_7_content','A Step-by-Step Guide on How to Register Your Property '),(1559,70,'_chapters_7_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1560,70,'chapters','8'),(1561,70,'_chapters','field_5afaa63036c3c'),(1562,70,'chapter1','41'),(1563,70,'_chapter1','field_5afabe9f63ba8'),(1564,70,'accordion-chapters_0_image','41'),(1565,70,'_accordion-chapters_0_image','field_5afac5ad447e0'),(1566,70,'accordion-chapters_0_content','<div class=\"container\">You might have decided to invest in real estate, but how do you find the right home to purchase? A glossy brochure can seem very attractive, but there are deeper aspects to look into before deciding whether a property will be a worthwhile investment. \r\n\r\nKnowing exactly what questions to ask before zeroing in on a property can be the difference between a good investment and a bad investment. \r\n\r\nA smart real estate purchase will deliver a high ROI margin while a bad real estate investment depreciates over time. For most ongoing projects, the factors that can influence price appreciation might not be immediately evident. This is why, understanding what to look for in a project can help you make the right decision. \r\n\r\nIf you have decided to take the leap into real estate investment, here are a few tips to follow.\r\n\r\n1. ASSESS YOUR NEEDS\r\n\r\nIf theres one thing home buyers have no shortage of, its the number of choices available in todays real estate market. The challenge then becomes not to find investment options, but to narrow them down. The two questions to ask yourself when looking for a home are:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full-width-bg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/chapter1-sub-image.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</br>\r\n2. Set Your Budget\r\n\r\nA home loan can only finance 80% of the total property value, so the remaining 20% needs to come from your personal finances. Before you set out on a house hunt, make a complete evaluation of your personal finances and decide how much you can realistically afford to spend on a home. \r\n\r\n3. Evaluate Your Options\r\n\r\nWith the huge number of projects coming up, the variety of residences available for home buyers have also increased. Typically, you can choose from three main types of residential properties:\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 text-center text-xs-center text-sm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n   <img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/apartments.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n   <p class=\"\">Apartments</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n   <img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/villas.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n   <p class=\"\">Villas</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n   <img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/villaments.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n   <p class=\"\">Villaments</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</br>\r\nBased on your budget and needs, you can decide which option is the best fit for you. \r\n\r\n4. Choose Your Location\r\n\r\nThe location of your new home is crucial both on a personal level and from an investment perspective.\r\n\r\nA few questions to ask yourself before deciding on a location are:\r\n\r\n	Does this locality attract investments from large corporations which can increase property 	\r\n	value over time?\r\n	How far is it from my workplace? \r\n	Is it close to essential facilities like hospitals, schools and colleges?\r\n	Does it have conveniences like supermarkets, banks and ATMs nearby?\r\n	Are there any recreational facilities like malls, multiplexes and restaurants nearby?\r\n\r\n5. Check Your Credit Score\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to apply for a home loan, as most home buyers do, your credit score, or CIBIL score, can be a make or break factor. The CIBIL score is based on your financial credit history and can be analysed through the following categories:\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bar.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),(1567,70,'_accordion-chapters_0_content','field_5afac5c5447e1'),(1568,70,'accordion-chapters','2'),(1569,70,'_accordion-chapters','field_5afac592447df'),(1570,70,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','CHAPTER 1'),(1571,70,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(1572,70,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing '),(1573,70,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(1574,70,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','CHAPTER 2'),(1575,70,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(1576,70,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(1577,70,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(1578,70,'accordion-chapters_1_image','50'),(1579,70,'_accordion-chapters_1_image','field_5afac5ad447e0'),(1580,70,'accordion-chapters_1_content','You might have decided to invest in real estate, but how do you find the right home to purchase? A glossy brochure can seem very attractive, but there are deeper aspects to look into before deciding whether a property will be a worthwhile investment. \r\n\r\nKnowing exactly what questions to ask before zeroing in on a property can be the difference between a good investment and a bad investment. \r\n\r\nA smart real estate purchase will deliver a high ROI margin while a bad real estate investment depreciates over time. For most ongoing projects, the factors that can influence price appreciation might not be immediately evident. This is why, understanding what to look for in a project can help you make the right decision. \r\n\r\nIf you have decided to take the leap into real estate investment, here are a few tips to follow.\r\n\r\n1. Assess Your Needs\r\n\r\nIf theres one thing home buyers have no shortage of, its the number of choices available in todays real estate market. The challenge then becomes not to find investment options, but to narrow them down. The two questions to ask yourself when looking for a home are:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full-width-bg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/chapter1-sub-image.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;\" alt=\"\" /></div>'),(1581,70,'_accordion-chapters_1_content','field_5afac5c5447e1'),(1582,71,'main-content','Being able to own a home of their own is often the biggest motivation for people to work hard and save money. In India, a home is more than just a piece of property, it is also a source of pride, security and stability. More Indians today are looking to invest in residential property, instead of living in rented houses as tenants.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"regular-pro-semibold\">The Economic Survey 2017-18 revealed that only 28% of urban Indians live in rented houses as compared to 1961 when as many as 54% lived in rented houses.</span>\r\n\r\nThe current Indian real estate market is booming, making it the perfect investment opportunity for almost guaranteed returns. Rapid improvements in infrastructural developments in the suburbs and increased competitiveness among property developers have given home buyers immense choice when it comes to finding a home to invest in. \r\n\r\nThese market conditions have also been supported by a slew of economic policies introduced by the government to make home ownership accessible to all. The RERA act was a landmark move to bring about transparency in the real estate sector and protect a buyers interests. The complex and highly variable tax structure in real estate was also eliminated with the introduction of GST, which standardised tax rates across the country. But, arguably, the most ambitious move to encourage more people to buy homes was the launch of the Housing for All scheme which offered heavily subsidised interest rates on home loans. This was one of the best first-time home buyer benefits to encourage more people to invest. \r\n\r\nThese factors have made this the perfect time to invest in a home of your own. However, for first-time home buyers, the entire process can seem confusing and intimidating. This in-depth home buyers guide will help you understand every step involved in the homebuying process and ensure that it goes smoothly.\r\n'),(1583,71,'_main-content','field_5afa9f11ebf40'),(1584,71,'chapters_0_image','35'),(1585,71,'_chapters_0_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1586,71,'chapters_0_title','Chapter 1'),(1587,71,'_chapters_0_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1588,71,'chapters_0_content','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(1589,71,'_chapters_0_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1590,71,'chapters_1_image','36'),(1591,71,'_chapters_1_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1592,71,'chapters_1_title','Chapter 2'),(1593,71,'_chapters_1_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1594,71,'chapters_1_content','Best Investment  Destinations to Buy a Home'),(1595,71,'_chapters_1_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1596,71,'chapters_2_image','37'),(1597,71,'_chapters_2_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1598,71,'chapters_2_title','Chapter 3'),(1599,71,'_chapters_2_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1600,71,'chapters_2_content','Types of Residential  Property'),(1601,71,'_chapters_2_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1602,71,'chapters_3_image','30'),(160