ch standardised tax rates across the country. But, arguably, the most ambitious move to encourage more people to buy homes was the launch of the Housing for All scheme which offered heavily subsidised interest rates on home loans. This was one of the best first-time home buyer benefits to encourage more people to invest.\r\n\r\nThese factors have made this the perfect time to invest in a home of your own. However, for first-time home buyers, the entire process can seem confusing and intimidating. This in-depth home buyers guide will help you understand every step involved in the homebuying process and ensure that it goes smoothly.'),(1727,73,'_main-content','field_5afa9f11ebf40'),(1728,73,'chapters_0_image','35'),(1729,73,'_chapters_0_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1730,73,'chapters_0_title','Chapter 1'),(1731,73,'_chapters_0_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1732,73,'chapters_0_content','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(1733,73,'_chapters_0_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1734,73,'chapters_1_image','36'),(1735,73,'_chapters_1_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1736,73,'chapters_1_title','Chapter 2'),(1737,73,'_chapters_1_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1738,73,'chapters_1_content','Best Investment  Destinations to Buy a Home'),(1739,73,'_chapters_1_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1740,73,'chapters_2_image','37'),(1741,73,'_chapters_2_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1742,73,'chapters_2_title','Chapter 3'),(1743,73,'_chapters_2_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1744,73,'chapters_2_content','Types of Residential  Property'),(1745,73,'_chapters_2_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1746,73,'chapters_3_image','30'),(1747,73,'_chapters_3_image','field_5afaa63b36c3d'),(1748,73,'chapters_3_title','Chapter 4'),(1749,73,'_chapters_3_title','field_5afaa64536c3e'),(1750,73,'chapters_3_content','Things to Check Before Booking a Home'),(1751,73,'_chapters_3_content','field_5afaa64c36c3f'),(1752,73,'chapters_4_image','31'),(1753,73,'_chapters_4_image','field_5afaa