 of projects coming up, the variety of residences available for home buyers have also increased. Typically, you can choose from three main types of residential properties:\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 text-center text-xs-center text-sm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/apartments.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"\">Apartments</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/villas.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"\">Villas</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/villaments.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"\">Villaments</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nBased on your budget and needs, you can decide which option is the best fit for you.\r\n\r\n4. Choose Your Location\r\n\r\nThe location of your new home is crucial both on a personal level and from an investment perspective.\r\n\r\nA few questions to ask yourself before deciding on a location are:\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">     Does this locality attract investments from large corporations which can increase property value over time?\r\nHow far is it from my workplace?\r\nIs it close to essential facilities like hospitals, schools and colleges?\r\nDoes it have conveniences like supermarkets, banks and ATMs nearby?\r\nAre there any recreational facilities like malls, multiplexes and restaurants nearby?</p>\r\n5. Check Your Credit Score\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to apply for a home loan, as most home buyers do, your credit score, or CIBIL score, can be a make or break factor. The CIBIL score is based on your financial credit history and can be analysed through the following categories:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center text-xs-center text-sm-center\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://localhost/shriram-pillar-page/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bar.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</div>\r\n</br>\r\nBanks might not approve your home loan application if it is low, so if you do have a bad CIBIL score, its a good idea to take steps to increase it before applying.\r\n\r\n6. Check Credibility of Builders\r\n\r\nMaking a real estate investment is not the best time to test your luck with a gamble. While unknown builders might attract you with lower prices, you can never be sure of their quality of construction, if they have the required approvals or if they will complete the project on time This is why, you should always choose a reputed builder to ensure that the process goes smoothly. \r\n\r\nFor more information on how to prepare for your house hunt, read 7 Things a First-Time Home Buyer Should Know Before Investing. \r\n</div>'),(2431,82,'_accordion-chapters_0_content','field_5afac5c5447e1'),(2432,82,'accordion-chapters','2'),(2433,82,'_accordion-chapters','field_5afac592447df'),(2434,82,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','CHAPTER 1'),(2435,82,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(2436,82,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing '),(2437,82,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(2438,82,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','CHAPTER 2'),(2439,82,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(2440,82,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(2441,82,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(2442,82,'accordion-chapters_1_image','50'),(2443,82,'_accordion-chapters_1_image','field_5afac5ad447e0'),(2444,82,'accordion-chapters_1_content','You might have decided to invest in real estate, but how do you find the right home to purchase? A glossy brochure can seem very attractive, but there are deeper aspects to look into before deciding whether a prope