ngs a First-Time Home Buyer Should Know Before Investing.\r\n\r\n</div>'),(2575,84,'_accordion-chapters_0_content','field_5afac5c5447e1'),(2576,84,'accordion-chapters','2'),(2577,84,'_accordion-chapters','field_5afac592447df'),(2578,84,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','CHAPTER 1'),(2579,84,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(2580,84,'accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing '),(2581,84,'_accordion-chapters_0_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(2582,84,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','CHAPTER 2'),(2583,84,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-number','field_5afac74e5acb2'),(2584,84,'accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','Things First-Time Home Buyers Should Know Before Investing'),(2585,84,'_accordion-chapters_1_chapter-title','field_5afac75b5acb3'),(2586,84,'accordion-chapters_1_image','50'),(2587,84,'_accordion-chapters_1_image','field_5afac5ad447e0'),(2588,84,'accordion-chapters_1_content','You might have decided to invest in real estate, but how do you find the right home to purchase? A glossy brochure can seem very attractive, but there are deeper aspects to look into before deciding whether a property will be a worthwhile investment.\r\n\r\nKnowing exactly what questions to ask before zeroing in on a property can be the difference between a good investment and a bad investment.\r\n\r\nA smart real estate purchase will deliver a high ROI margin while a bad real estate investment depreciates over time. For most ongoing projects, the factors that can influence price appreciation might not be immediately evident. This is why, understanding what to look for in a project can help you make the right decision.\r\n\r\nIf you have decided to take the leap into real estate investment, here are a few tips to follow.\r\n\r\n1. Assess Your Needs\r\n\r\nIf theres one thing home buyers have no shortage of, its the number of choices available in todays real estate market. The challenge then b